  Garba Marafa’s faction, Alhaji Surajo  Maikafako is the only registered member of his faction, saying that out of the 140 members he claims to be his members are not registered members of the party. “I want to make it very clear that Maikatako is not recognized by the national headquarters of the party and he does not even represent Zamfara state chapter of the party” Continuing, Barrister Umar explained that there are 160 people were invited by the committee to appear before it on September 7th, 2020. Vanguard The warring factions of the ruling All Progressives Congress (APC) in Kogi state are to face a reconciliation committee inaugurated by the party. August 22, 2017 In "News" The Zamfara Chapter of the All Progressives Congress (APC) has sets up a nine-man technical committee to draft development plans of the party in the state. News Agency of Nigeria (NAN) reports that the state chairman of the party, Alhaji Lawal Liman, inaugurated the committee at the party secretariat in… September 20, 2019 In "News" The Chief Cyril Ogodo-led Executive Committee of the Delta state chapter of the All Progressives Congress (APC) has protested to the National Chairman of the party, Comrade Adams Oshiomhole, not to allow what it described as a fraudulent hijack of the party structures in the state by those not duly… July 3, 2018 In "News"